shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Artboard_17-100.jpg","badge":"","time":"","title":"Parent's Bag","text":"<p>Offers stylish storage for all your essentials. With a sleek design that complements your Bentley Trike, it features ample space for snacks, toys, and personal items. It keeps everything within reach during your strolls.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_UMznCd":{"type":"toggle","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/05.jpg","badge":"","time":"","title":"Magnetic Buckle","text":"<p>The up-to-date \"Bentley\" labeled magnetic buckle combined with the elastic 5-point belt ensures optimal safety and trust from one hand and the simplicity of usage from another.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_6anEEk":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Artboard_14-100_12066400-a4dc-48b7-a963-e9136ec7bce2.jpg","badge":"","time":"","title":"Handlebar Grips","text":"<p>This trike carries forward a signature touch of luxury with leather inserts on the handlebar grips, safety guard, and parent remote control — ensuring comfort and elegance in every ride.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_LnUXnj":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Artboard_11-100.jpg","badge":"","time":"","title":"Replica Continental GT Mulliner Wheels","text":"<p>The tricycle’s wheels precisely replicate the iconic Mulliner GT rims, complete with the Bentley logo at the center and \"Bentley Mulliner\" engraving. <br\/><br\/>For an exclusive touch, the self-leveling wheel cap keeps the Bentley \"B\" upright as it moves — a true masterpiece in motion.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_8kFNXA":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Artboard_7-100.jpg","badge":"","time":"","title":"Anti-Slide Pedals","text":"<p>The new metal pedals with anti-slide surface design to prevent accidents.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}}},"block_order":["toggle_QMVnUf","toggle_nbemMh","toggle_J7U8zB","toggl